author: billbarker
msg: Adding a flag to disable setting a seperate time-out for uploads.

The effect of this is to have many fewer calls to setSoTimeout.  I've never seen that it makes much of a difference (at least on Solaris), but it shouldn't cause any problems as long as you don't plan on doing any big uploads.
